originalText.text:
When I first met Michele, she was extremely excited to show people what she saw in me. "Things I could not see".. Michele introduced me to social media, teaching me confidence, I could do it for myself! Later, on a special road trip again Michele teaching me some very valuable lessons. To set boundaries, to trust and love myself first.  I will always be grateful for my friend that taught me to see. The friend that saw and believed in me moving forward
In Gratitude,
Laura Sheldrick
Anitye Consulting

originalText.text: She has created a magical embrace for those feeling lost within. Inspired by her life journey, courage, and deep love for other, I've had the privilege of working with Michele on a one on one retreat. She has transformed my life. The 7 Stages of Grief Alignment is a much required topic to embrace. Whatever formula she uses to create such a meaningful retreat was healing from the moment we spoke. Michele is a gifted healer. I've never met anyone who deeply touched my soul on so many levels.

originalText.text:
Many people process differently during the healing journey, but for Michele, she heals daily within a space of mind, body, and spirit.
You can immediately feel the shift with one big hug from this women.
Her spirit is powerful. She is a powerhouse!
I honestly believe as a healer myself, we are heart-fully guided by spirit. We are the conduit in finding joy and facilitator in helping others confront the demons that keep us from experiencing the joys of life.
Michele has this innate ability to embrace everyone she meets with unconditional love. What a blessing to share this journey with such a beautiful and genuine soul. Totally committed to her life purpose...
I was honored to be a part of her first Holistic Expo in New York! It was truly a success watching everyone come together in community.
